      "raw_text": "\n\n# I AM THE CHANGE\n\n## Scholarship Program \u2014 Home Visit Questionnaire\n\nTeam Everest | Confidential\n\nVolunteer Name:\n\nCo-Volunteer Name:\n\nDate of Visit:\n\nVENKATA NARAYANA G.V.\n\nCHANDRA MOHAN\n\n20 JUN - 2026\n\n## Section 1 \u2014 Student Profile\n\n### 1.1. Application ID\n\nEnter application ID\n\nTEMP -2026 -8363\n\n### 1.2. Student Full Name\n\nEnter full name\n\nGOKUL C\n\n### 1.3. Gender\n\n\u2612 Male\n\n\u2610 Female\n\n\u2610 Others\n\n## Section 2 \u2014 Family Background\n\n### 2.1. Family Status\n\n\u2612 Single Parent\n\n\u2610 Parentless\n\n\u2610 Having both parents\n\n### 2.2. Relationship Details (if applicable)\n\n| Year of Death / Separation | Reason for Death / Separation |\n|----------------------------|-------------------------------|\n| 2024                       | HEART ATTACK                  |\n\n### 2.3. Is Father/ Mother photograph kept at home?\n\n\u2612 Yes \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 No\n\n### 2.4. Government ID Verified (Ration Card / Aadhaar / Driving Licence / Voter ID)\n\n\u2612 Aadhaar Card \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Ration Card \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Driving Licence \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Voter ID\n\n\u2610 Other: \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\n\n### 2.5. Family Members\n\n| Name           | Age | Education       | Occupation    | Annual Income |\n|----------------|-----|-----------------|---------------|---------------|\n| Senthilmani. C | 42  | 8 <sup>th</sup> | HOUSE KEEPING | 84,000        |\n| NIVINIEHA. C   | 19  | B.A Eco         | \u2014             |               |\n|                |     |                 |               |               |\n|                |     |                 |               |               |\n\n## Section 3 \u2014 Housing Condition\n\n### 3.1. House Ownership\n\n\u2612 Own \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Rented\n\n#### \n\n--- Page 2 ---\n\n3.1.1 If rented, what is the rent amount?\n\nRent amount: \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\n\n### 3.2. Type of Home\n\n\u2610 Individual \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Private Apartment \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Housing Board \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2612 Line House \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610\n\nOthers: \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\n\n### 3.3. Type of Ceiling\n\n- \u2610 Roof (Kurai) \u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Tiled \u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Asbestos / Sheet \u00a0\u00a0 \u2612 Concrete\n\n### 3.4. Number of Bedrooms\n\nEnter number 1\n\n#### \n\n--- Page 3 ---\n\n3.4.1 Type of Bedroom\n\n- \u2612 Separate Bedroom \u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 No Separate Bedroom\n\n### 3.5. Bathroom\n\n- \u2610 Separate \u00a0\u00a0 \u2612 Common for Apartment\n\n### 3.6. Kitchen Type\n\n- \u2610 Separate Kitchen \u00a0\u00a0 \u2612 Hall with Kitchen\n\n## Section 4 \u2014 Financial Background\n\n### 4.1. Assets at Home (tick all that apply)\n\n- \u2612 Washing Machine \u00a0\u00a0 \u2612 Fridge \u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 AC \u00a0\u00a0 \u2612 LED TV \u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Two-Wheeler \u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Car\n- \u2612 Smartphone \u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Separate Wi-Fi \u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Others: \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\n\n### 4.2. Amount of Last Electricity Bill\n\nAmount in \u20b9 238\n\n### 4.3. Do you own any other assets/properties in the name of grandparents, parents, or student?\n\n- \u2610 Yes \u00a0\u00a0 \u2612 No\n\n4.3.1 If yes, list their properties:\n\n| Property Description | Owner Name | Approximate Value |\n|----------------------|------------|-------------------|\n|                      |            |                   |\n|                      |            |                   |\n\n4.4. Apart from your job, is there any other source of income?\n\n\u2610 Yes \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2612 No\n\n4.4.1 If yes, list other sources of income:\n\n| Source of Income        | Amount |\n|-------------------------|--------|\n| HOUSE KEEPING IN SCHOOL | 7000/M |\n\n4.5. Income Type\n\n\u2612 Monthly \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Daily \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Weekly \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2610 Ad-Hoc\n\n4.6. Do you have any loans?\n\n\u2610 Yes \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u2612 No\n\n4.6.1 If yes, share Loan Purpose, Amount Taken, and Pending Loan Amount:\n\n| Sr. No. | Loan Purpose | Loan Amount Taken | Pending Loan Amount |\n|---------|--------------|-------------------|---------------------|\n|         |              |                   |                     |\n|         |              |                   |                     |\n|         |              |                   |                     |\n\n4.7. If you choose any college, how much is the college fee?\n\nAmount in \u20b9\n\n62,000\n\n4.8. If the college fee is higher, how will you manage it?\n\nPLANNING TO DO PART TIME JOB\n\n4.9. If you do not receive this scholarship, how will you pay the fees?\n\nPART TIME JOB AFTER COLLEGE HOURS\n\n## Section 5 \u2014 Health Information\n\n5.1. Does the student have any health issues?\n\n\u2610 Yes\n\n\u2612 No\n\n5.2. If yes, list the health issues:\n\nDescribe health issues\n\n## Section 6 \u2014 Student Commitment\n\n6.1. Will you study college for three years without any obstacle?\n\nYES\n\n6.2. If we have a training program within 15 km from your home, can you come?\n\n\u2612 Yes\n\n\u2610 No\n\n\u2610 Maybe\n\n6.3. Are you ready to send your son/daughter to weekly skill development classes on Sundays (16 classes a year)?\n\n\u2612 Yes \u2610 No\n\n## Section 7 \u2014 Scholarship Information\n\n7.1. Has the student received or applied for any other scholarships for their UG degree?\n\nNo\n\n## Section 8 \u2014 Volunteer Observation\n\n8.1. What is your opinion about the student, their family members, and their living condition?\n\nStudent is living with his mother & sister, his father was passed away, It is like house only one part of house belongs to them because they are a joint family, the condition is poor.\n\n8.2. Will you recommend this student for this scholarship?\n\n\u2612 Yes \u2610 No \u2610 Not Sure\n\n8.3. Any other comments you want to share?\n\nStudent need scholarship to pursue his degree.\n\n![Signature of S. Chandramohan](104fbf564e2e5a8fbd84f31656d114c7_img.jpg)  \n(S. CHANDRAMOHAN)\n\nVolunteer Signature\n\n![Signature of G.V. Venkatarayana](b538fe54c1f3a7343e37e85cc2d00497_img.jpg)\n\nCo-Volunteer Signature",
